e</code> if the number is even.</p><p class=\"pf-v6-c-content--p pf-m-editorial\">This prevents a next step from being executed as long as the number is not even.</p><form class=\"pf-v6-c-form\" novalidate=\"\" data-pfcsfrm=\"211ba9de-d456-4169-a948-687cd568c2fc\" on-detach-uid=\"d-id-206\"><div class=\"pf-v6-c-form__group\" data-identifier=\"wizard-hap-nh\" data-pfcsfrmfg=\"8ca5b002-44f4-419c-a082-fe7f3b598efa\" on-detach-uid=\"d-id-207\"><div class=\"pf-v6-c-form__group-label\" on-detach-uid=\"d-id-209\"><label class=\"pf-v6-c-form__label\" for=\"wizard-hap-nh\"><span class=\"pf-v6-c-form__label-text\">Number</span></label></div><div class=\"pf-v6-c-form__group-control\" on-detach-uid=\"d-id-211\"><span class=\"pf-v6-c-form-control\"><input type=\"number\" id=\"wizard-hap-nh\" name=\"wizard-hap-nh\" aria-invalid=\"false\"></span><div class=\"pf-v6-c-form__helper-text\"><div class=\"pf-v6-c-helper-text\"><div class=\"pf-v6-c-helper-text__item\"><span class=\"pf-v6-c-helper-text__item-text\">Enter an even number<span class=\"pf-v6-screen-reader\">: default_ status;</span></span></div></div></div></div></div></form></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"display: none;\"><div class=\"pf-v6-c-wizard__main-body\"><div class=\"pf-v6-l-flex pf-m-column pf-m-gap-md\"><div class=\"pf-v6-l-flex__item\"><p class=\"pf-v6-c-content--p pf-m-editorial\">This step has a <code>WizardStepNextPromise</code> that simulates cooking a meal and you can decide whether you get something to eat or not.</p><div class=\"pf-v6-l-flex pf-m-row pf-m-gap-md pf-m-align-items-center\"><div class=\"pf-v6-l-flex__item\"><label class=\"pf-v6-c-switch\" for=\"wizard-hap-np\" on-detach-uid=\"d-id-223\"><input type=\"checkbox\" class=\"pf-v6-c-switch__input\" id=\"wizard-hap-np\" name=\"wizard-hap-np\" role=\"switch\" aria-labelledby=\"wizard-hap-np-label\"><span class=\"pf-v6-c-switch__toggle\"></span><span class=\"pf-v6-c-switch__label\" id=\"wizard-hap-np-label\" aria-hidden=\"true\">Be a good chef.</spa